<p><b>Who is the wife of Ronaldo?</b> Georgina Rodríguez Hernández (born 27 January 1994) is an Argentine-born Spanish social media influencer and model. She is known for her relationship with footballer Cristiano Ronaldo. Rodriguez was the subject of an eponymous 2022 Netflix documentary, I Am Georgina, in which she was credited as the producer.</p>
